text: Gokul Prasad Baskota is a Nepalese politician and former Minister of Communication and Information Technology. He served as Minister of Communication and Information Technology of Nepal. He is a Member of the House of Representatives (Nepal) elected from Kavrepalanchok-2, Province No. 3. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Government ministers of Nepal
title: Gokul Prasad Baskota
